{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840803911,"sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","part":{"id":"prt_d785c2351001iR4yYbkCErOLij","messageID":"msg_d785c1186001YdT2zvP3pChbZ1","sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c702bee0391541698e04d61a78c375b9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: <!-- TODO: Fill in design details at Stage ST-1 -->\n18: \n19: ### Architecture\n20: \n21: 共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n22: - 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n23: - 常量使用统一命名规范（LabelKey*, AnnotationKey*, ConditionType*）\n24: - 默认值常量供 controller 使用\n25: \n26: ### Dependencies\n27: \n28: | Package | Purpose |\n29: |---------|---------|\n30: | (无外部依赖) | 共享类型为基础定义 |\n31: \n32: ### Controller-gen Markers\n33: \n34: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n35: |--------|------------|---------|\n36: | `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType | 枚举验证 |\n37: | `+kubebuilder:default` | TargetPort.Protocol | 默认值 |\n38: \n39: ## Data Structures\n40: \n41: <!-- TODO: Fill in data structure details at Stage ST-1 -->\n42: \n43: ### Shared Types\n44: \n45: ```go\n46: // ProtocolType defines the protocol for a target port.\n47: type ProtocolType string\n48: \n49: const (\n50:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n51:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n52: )\n53: \n54: // AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for a CodeInterpreter.\n55: type AuthModeType string\n56: \n57: const (\n58:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n59:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n60: )\n61: \n62: // TargetPort defines a network port configuration for exposing sandbox services.\n63: type TargetPort struct {\n64:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n65:     Name       string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n66:     Port       uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n67:     Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n68: }\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ### Constants (To Be Defined)\n72: \n73: <!-- TODO: Define specific constants at Stage ST-1 -->\n74: \n75: - Label Constants\n76: - Annotation Constants\n77: - Condition Type Constants\n78: - Default Value Constants\n79: \n80: ## Testing Strategy\n81: \n82: <!-- TODO: Fill in testing strategy at Stage ST-1 -->\n83: \n84: ## File Structure\n85: \n86: ```\n87: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n88:   shared_types.go — 共享类型、枚举、常量\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ## References\n92: \n93: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n94: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n95: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 95 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n<!-- TODO: Fill in design details at Stage ST-1 -->\n\n### Architecture\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775840803880,"end":1775840803910}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840803913,"sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","part":{"id":"prt_d785c273a0016HFLz4B9sRnFkN","messageID":"msg_d785c1186001YdT2zvP3pChbZ1","sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-354aa694c1ae46f79eafd5ba663c9e85","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n16: - `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n17: - `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n18: - `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n19: - Label/Annotation 常量\n20: - Condition Type 常量\n21: - 默认值常量\n22: \n23: ## Out of Scope\n24: \n25: - Controller 实现\n26: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n27: - CRD YAML 生成\n28: - client-go 代码生成\n29: \n30: ## Dependencies\n31: \n32: 无外部依赖，为 AR-001、AR-002 提供共享类型。\n33: \n34: ## Deliverables\n35: \n36: | File | Description |\n37: |------|-------------|\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 共享类型和常量定义 |\n39: \n40: ## Acceptance Criteria\n41: \n42: - [ ] 共享类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n43: - [ ] 常量命名遵循统一命名规范\n44: - [ ] 包含完整的 godoc 注释\n45: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n46: - [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n47: \n48: ## References\n49: \n50: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n51: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n52: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n- `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n- `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n- Label/Annotation 常量\n- Condition Type 常量","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840803883,"end":1775840803912}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840803914,"sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","part":{"id":"prt_d785c2b77001uneJNAWIbWl1cV","messageID":"msg_d785c1186001YdT2zvP3pChbZ1","sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ab5cf6560d034d31a672a130a29b7925","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Define shared types, constants, and common utilities for CRD type definitions in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. These shared elements provide:\n6: \n7: 1. **Common Type Definitions**: Shared structs used across multiple CRDs (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType)\n8: 2. **Label/Annotation Constants**: Standard labels and annotations for sandbox resources\n9: 3. **Condition Types**: Standard condition type constants for status reporting\n10: 4. **Validation Helpers**: Shared validation constants and patterns\n11: \n12: ## Scope\n13: \n14: ### In Scope\n15: \n16: | Deliverable | Description |\n17: |-------------|-------------|\n18: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Shared type definitions (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType) |\n19: | Label/Annotation constants | Standard labels/annotations for sandbox lifecycle |\n20: | Condition type constants | Standard condition types for status reporting |\n21: | Default value constants | Default timeout/duration constants |\n22: \n23: ### Type Definitions Required\n24: \n25: #### Shared Types (Already Defined)\n26: \n27: - `TargetPort`: Port configuration with pathPrefix, name, port, protocol\n28: - `ProtocolType`: Enum for HTTP/HTTPS\n29: - `AuthModeType`: Enum for picod/none\n30: \n31: #### Constants to Define\n32: \n33: - **Label Constants**: Sandbox owner labels, runtime type labels\n34: - **Annotation Constants**: Session tracking, authentication annotations\n35: - **Condition Types**: Ready, Available, Progressing, Degraded\n36: - **Default Values**: Session timeout, max session duration defaults\n37: \n38: ### Out of Scope\n39: \n40: - Controller implementation (`pkg/controllers/`)\n41: - Webhook validation logic\n42: - CRD YAML generation (handled by `make gen-crd`)\n43: - client-go code generation (handled by `make gen-client`)\n44: - AgentRuntime CRD (AR-001)\n45: - CodeInterpreter CRD (AR-002)\n46: \n47: ## Impact Analysis\n48: \n49: ### Upstream Dependencies\n50: \n51: | Dependency | Impact |\n52: |------------|--------|\n53: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | Required for metav1.Condition type constants |\n54: \n55: ### Downstream Consumers\n56: \n57: | Consumer | Usage |\n58: |----------|-------|\n59: | AR-001 AgentRuntime | Uses TargetPort, ProtocolType |\n60: | AR-002 CodeInterpreter | Uses TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType |\n61: | Workload Manager | Uses label/annotation constants |\n62: | Router | Uses condition type constants for status checks |\n63: \n64: ## Alternatives Considered\n65: \n66: | Alternative | Pros | Cons | Decision |\n67: |-------------|------|------|----------|\n68: | **Inline constants per CRD** | Localized definition | Duplication, inconsistency | Rejected |\n69: | **Separate constants package** | Decoupled constants | Import complexity | Rejected - keep in shared_types.go |\n70: | **Generated constants** | Automated consistency | Over-engineering for S-size | Rejected |\n71: \n72: ## Risks\n73: \n74: | Risk | Mitigation |\n75: |------|------------|\n76: | Constant naming conflicts | Use package prefix pattern |\n77: | Breaking constant changes | Document stability expectations |\n78: | Condition type proliferation | Define minimal set initially |\n79: \n80: ## Implementation Notes\n81: \n82: 1. **Naming Convention**: Use `LabelKey*`, `AnnotationKey*`, `ConditionType*` patterns\n83: 2. **Documentation**: Add godoc comments for all constants\n84: 3. **Location**: All constants in `shared_types.go` for easy discovery\n85: 4. **Stability**: Mark constants with stability expectations\n86: \n87: ## References\n88: \n89: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n90: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n91: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n92: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 92 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine shared types, constants, and common utilities for CRD type definitions in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. These shared elements provide:\n\n1. **Common Type Definitions**: Shared structs used across multiple CRDs (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType)\n2. **Label/Annotation Constants**: Standard labels and annotations for sandbox resources\n3. **Condition Types**: Standard condition type constants for status reporting\n4. **Validation Helpers**: Shared validation constants and patterns\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Shared type definitions (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType) |\n| Label/Annotation constants | Standard labels/annotations for sandbox lifecycle |\n| Condition type constants | Standard condition types for status reporting |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775840803885,"end":1775840803913}}}}
