{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840907212,"sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","part":{"id":"prt_d785dcf670015PSoyMMsX4LgI3","messageID":"msg_d785c891a001eBcB0CoM217K0O","sessionID":"ses_287a41719ffe3yjKakA0SJdIoO","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-824c7b4adeab409e99b2cf0cab7e8524","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n- 常量使用统一命名规范（LabelKey*, AnnotationKey*, ConditionType*）\n- 默认值常量供 controller 使用\n- 所有定义位于 `shared_types.go`，便于集中管理\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| (无外部依赖) | 共享类型为基础定义 |\n\n### Controller-gen Markers\n\n| Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n|--------|------------|---------|\n| `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType | 枚举验证 |\n| `+kubebuilder:default` | TargetPort.Protocol | 默认值 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Shared Types\n\n#### ProtocolType\n\n```go\n// ProtocolType defines the protocol for a target port.\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    // ProtocolTypeHTTP indicates HTTP protocol.\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    // ProtocolTypeHTTPS indicates HTTPS protocol.\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n```\n\n#### AuthModeType\n\n```go\n// AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for a CodeInterpreter.\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    // AuthModePicoD indicates pico authentication mode.\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    // AuthModeNone indicates no authentication.\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n#### TargetPort\n\n```go\n// TargetPort defines a network port configuration for exposing sandbox services.\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // PathPrefix is the URL path prefix for routing to this port.\n    // +optional\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Name is a human-readable name for this port.\n    // +optional\n    Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Port is the container port number to expose.\n    Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n\n    // Protocol specifies the protocol for this port (HTTP or HTTPS).\n    // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n    Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Constants\n\n#### Label Constants\n\nLabels 用于标识沙箱资源的元数据，遵循 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/<key>` 格式：\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // LabelKeyOwnerRuntime indicates the owning AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter name.\n    LabelKeyOwnerRuntime = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n\n    // LabelKeyOwnerKind indicates the owning CRD kind (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter).\n    LabelKeyOwnerKind = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n\n    // LabelKeySessionID indicates the active session identifier.\n    LabelKeySessionID = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n\n    // LabelKeySandboxType indicates the sandbox type (agent/code-interpreter).\n    LabelKeySandboxType = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n\n    // LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent indicates an agent sandbox.\n    LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent = \"agent\"\n\n    // LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter indicates a code interpreter sandbox.\n    LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter = \"code-interpreter\"\n)\n```\n\n#### Annotation Constants\n\nAnnotations 用于存储运行时配置和状态信息：\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // AnnotationKeyAuthMode stores the authentication mode for the sandbox.\n    AnnotationKeyAuthMode = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n\n    // AnnotationKeySessionStart stores the session start timestamp.\n    AnnotationKeySessionStart = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n\n    // AnnotationKeySessionEnd stores the session end timestamp.\n    AnnotationKeySessionEnd = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n\n    // AnnotationKeyLastActivity stores the last activity timestamp.\n    AnnotationKeyLastActivity = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n\n    // AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember indicates if pod is part of warm pool.\n    AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n)\n```\n\n#### Condition Type Constants\n\nCondition types 用于 status.conditions 数组，遵循 Kubernetes Condition pattern：\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // ConditionTypeReady indicates the runtime is ready to accept sessions.\n    ConditionTypeReady = \"Ready\"\n\n    // ConditionTypeAvailable indicates the runtime is available for use.\n    ConditionTypeAvailable = \"Available\"\n\n    // ConditionTypeProgressing indicates the runtime is being created/updated.\n    ConditionTypeProgressing = \"Progressing\"\n\n    // ConditionTypeDegraded indicates the runtime is in a degraded state.\n    ConditionTypeDegraded = \"Degraded\"\n\n    // ConditionTypeSessionActive indicates an active session is running.\n    ConditionTypeSessionActive = \"SessionActive\"\n)\n```\n\n#### Condition Reason Constants\n\nCondition reasons 描述 condition 状态变化的原因：\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // ConditionReasonRunning indicates the runtime is running normally.\n    ConditionReasonRunning = \"Running\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonCreating indicates the runtime is being created.\n    ConditionReasonCreating = \"Creating\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonUpdating indicates the runtime is being updated.\n    ConditionReasonUpdating = \"Updating\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonDeleting indicates the runtime is being deleted.\n    ConditionReasonDeleting = \"Deleting\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonError indicates an error occurred.\n    ConditionReasonError = \"Error\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonTimeout indicates a timeout occurred.\n    ConditionReasonTimeout = \"Timeout\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonSessionStarted indicates a session has started.\n    ConditionReasonSessionStarted = \"SessionStarted\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonSessionEnded indicates a session has ended.\n    ConditionReasonSessionEnded = \"SessionEnded\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonIdleTimeout indicates session ended due to idle timeout.\n    ConditionReasonIdleTimeout = \"IdleTimeout\"\n\n    // ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached indicates session ended due to max duration.\n    ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n)\n```\n\n#### Default Value Constants\n\n默认值常量供 controller 初始化配置使用：\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // DefaultSessionTimeout is the default idle session timeout (15 minutes).\n    DefaultSessionTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n\n    // DefaultMaxSessionDuration is the default maximum session duration (8 hours).\n    DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8 * time.Hour\n\n    // DefaultWarmPoolSize is the default warm pool size for CodeInterpreter.\n    DefaultWarmPoolSize = 0\n\n    // DefaultAuthMode is the default authentication mode.\n    DefaultAuthMode = AuthModePicoD\n\n    // DefaultProtocol is the default protocol for TargetPort.\n    DefaultProtocol = ProtocolTypeHTTP\n)\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Label Contract\n\n| Label Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n|-----------|--------------|------------|\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime` | CR name | Pod, Service |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind` | `AgentRuntime` / `CodeInterpreter` | Pod, Service |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id` | UUID | Pod (active session) |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type` | `agent` / `code-interpreter` | Pod |\n\n### Annotation Contract\n\n| Annotation Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n|-----------------|--------------|------------|\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode` | `picod` / `none` | Pod |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member` | `true` / `false` | Pod |\n\n### Condition Contract\n\n| Condition Type | Meaning | True Condition |\n|-----------------|---------|----------------|\n| `Ready` | Runtime ready for sessions | Pod running, no errors |\n| `Available` | Runtime available | Ready + healthy |\n| `Progressing` | Runtime being modified | Creation/update in progress |\n| `Degraded` | Runtime in degraded state | Errors present |\n| `SessionActive` | Session running | Pod has active session |\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Validation Errors\n\n| Error Type | Trigger | Response |\n|------------|---------|----------|\n| Invalid ProtocolType | Value not `HTTP`/`HTTPS` | API server rejects with 400 |\n| Invalid AuthModeType | Value not `picod`/`none` | API server rejects with 400 |\n| Missing required Port | Port field empty | API server rejects with 400 |\n| Invalid port number | Port > 65535 | Controller webhook rejects |\n\n### Controller Error Handling\n\n| Error Type | Handling |\n|------------|----------|\n| Label/Annotation conflict | Log warning, use CR-specified value |\n| Condition update failure | Retry with exponential backoff |\n| Default value override | Use CR spec value if specified |\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| Enum constants | Verify all enum values match expected strings |\n| DeepCopy | TargetPort.DeepCopy creates independent copy |\n| JSON serialization | TargetPort JSON tags correct (camelCase) |\n| Default values | Verify default constants match spec defaults |\n\n### Test Cases\n\n```go\nfunc TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    tests := []struct {\n        name     string\n        constant ProtocolType\n        expected string\n    }{\n        {\"HTTP\", ProtocolTypeHTTP, \"HTTP\"},\n        {\"HTTPS\", ProtocolTypeHTTPS, \"HTTPS\"},\n    }\n    for _, tt := range tests {\n        if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n            t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    tests := []struct {\n        name     string\n        constant AuthModeType\n        expected string\n    }{\n        {\"PicoD\", AuthModePicoD, \"picod\"},\n        {\"None\", AuthModeNone, \"none\"},\n    }\n    for _, tt := range tests {\n        if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n            t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestTargetPortDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n    original := &TargetPort{\n        PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n        Name:       \"api\",\n        Port:       8080,\n        Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n    }\n    copy := original.DeepCopy()\n    \n    if copy == original {\n        t.Error(\"DeepCopy returned same pointer\")\n    }\n    if copy.PathPrefix != original.PathPrefix {\n        t.Error(\"PathPrefix not copied correctly\")\n    }\n    \n    copy.PathPrefix = \"/modified\"\n    if original.PathPrefix == \"/modified\" {\n        t.Error(\"DeepCopy is not deep\")\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestTargetPortJSONSerialization(t *testing.T) {\n    tp := TargetPort{\n        PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n        Name:       \"api\",\n        Port:       8080,\n        Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n    }\n    data, err := json.Marshal(tp)\n    if err != nil {\n        t.Fatalf(\"marshal failed: %v\", err)\n    }\n    expected := `{\"pathPrefix\":\"/api\",\"name\":\"api\",\"port\":8080,\"protocol\":\"HTTP\"}`\n    if string(data) != expected {\n        t.Errorf(\"expected %s, got %s\", expected, string(data))\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestLabelConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    if LabelKeyOwnerRuntime != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\" {\n        t.Error(\"LabelKeyOwnerRuntime mismatch\")\n    }\n    if LabelKeySessionID != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\" {\n        t.Error(\"LabelKeySessionID mismatch\")\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestConditionTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    if ConditionTypeReady != \"Ready\" {\n        t.Error(\"ConditionTypeReady mismatch\")\n    }\n    if ConditionTypeAvailable != \"Available\" {\n        t.Error(\"ConditionTypeAvailable mismatch\")\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestDefaultConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    if DefaultSessionTimeout != 15*time.Minute {\n        t.Error(\"DefaultSessionTimeout mismatch\")\n    }\n    if DefaultMaxSessionDuration != 8*time.Hour {\n        t.Error(\"DefaultMaxSessionDuration mismatch\")\n    }\n    if DefaultAuthMode != AuthModePicoD {\n        t.Error(\"DefaultAuthMode mismatch\")\n    }\n    if DefaultProtocol != ProtocolTypeHTTP {\n        t.Error(\"DefaultProtocol mismatch\")\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- Verify labels/annotations applied to pods match constant definitions\n- Verify conditions in CRD status use defined type constants\n- Verify CRD YAML generation includes enum validation\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  shared_types.go      — 共享类型、枚举、常量定义\n  zz_generated.deepcopy.go — DeepCopy 方法（由 controller-gen 生成）\n  types_test.go        — 单元测试\n```\n\n### shared_types.go Structure\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"time\"\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Type Definitions\n// ============================================================================\n\ntype ProtocolType string\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string    